version_description: This is an exact representation of the acoustic and electric parts of the song. Note that all verses but the first have an electric in the background picking around the verse chords.
I'm correcting a different version. I promise this is right.

This version is more in depth with the variation of chords that Dean liked to play, especially on the record and including the Unplugged. The E Minor chord is slightly modified as well, and barre chords are used more frequently in this.
